name: Cosco_4_Pack_Resin_Folding_Chair_
reviews: I was having a house full of company and needed to order folding chairs that would be comfortable, safe and wouldn't cost a fortune. These were perfect. I shopped locally in the big box stores and their prices were much higher. I was definitely very pleased with the quality when I received them.
description: These Cosco high-quality, low-maintenance chairs are ideal for any gathering both indoor and outdoor. Featuring durable steel frames and solid construction. Chairs have a molded resin seat and back. Features a folding frame and lightweight feel. Pull these chairs out for company when you host a big dinner or other event. The molded seats deliver added comfort during use, and the solid frame adds strength and resilience to the design.
